      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for a buyer looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The engine runs and the car is drivable, but it does show significant signs of wear, including some noticeable scratches on the body and interior upholstery that has seen better days. Mechanically, it would benefit from a tune-up and some minor repairs to bring it back to its best. It\u2019s an honest car at an honest price for someone willing to put in a little elbow grease.",
