    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and totally ready for its next adventure. I've taken great care of it, so it runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway. It's the perfect balance of quality and value\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
