      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has plenty of life left for its next adventure! I've taken good care of it, so you\u2019re getting a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. Perfect for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin!",
