      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including professional subframe reinforcement and a recent valve clearance adjustment. The double-VANOS system operates within factory specifications, and the cooling system has been overhauled with an aluminum radiator. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the chassis remains rigid with refreshed bushings and precise steering feedback. A driver-focused machine with robust mechanical vitals.",
